{"tid":1108272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貪玩出事】小兄妹拎電動剃刀當玩具 媽媽睇見「癩痢頭」好傷心","createTime":"2019-04-16T00:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T04:32:21.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5f364b932efa415c6c3686055c22578fb78eddc1","tid":1108272,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T00:00:54.000Z","msg":"小孩子不時在家中搗亂，美國德州有對小兄妹誤打誤撞找到媽媽的電動剃刀，於是自行理髮，結果把頭剃得像癩痢。媽媽傷心得哭了出來，最後要為他們剃光頭補救。<br />\n利克（Stephie Leigh）在Instagram分享泰迪（Teddy）及艾蘿依（Eloise）的「傑作」，泰迪不規則地剃走自己一撮又一撮的頭髮，艾蘿依的正面看似沒事，不過一轉身就見到後腦的頭髮幾乎全被剃光，只剩下兩條小辮子。<br />\n利克起初接受不了事實哭了出來，後來也說：「也只是頭髮，好吧那只是頭髮，會長回來的，媽媽沒事了。為何妳讓哥哥這樣做呢？」泰迪還天真無邪地表示：「她說非常喜歡我那樣做（剃頭），所以我就剃了，我們想給妳看看。」<br />\n不過艾蘿依被問到是否喜歡自己的新髮型時，小妮子如實回答：「不喜歡。媽咪我看來像個男孩子，媽咪妳可不可以將妳的頭髮給我？」利克安慰她說她仍很漂亮，不似男孩子，泰迪也安慰妹妹道：「妳的臉仍像個女孩。」<br />\n利克後來發現仍是嬰兒的幼子也被剃頭，頭頂毛髮被剃走一大片。她之後索性為泰迪及艾蘿依剃光頭，他們似乎也蠻喜歡自己的清涼新髮型。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190415/large/1555314398_7cc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190415%2Flarge%2F1555314398_7cc9.jpg&h=948f0647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190415/large/1555317272_818f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190415%2Flarge%2F1555317272_818f.jpg&h=a760c689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190415/59489823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190415%2F59489823&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCdy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=54509200\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190415%2F59489823&h=f9358de5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190415/59489823</a>"},{"pid":"6d18b20ca6beb2d447662d8f69eb2694a43aa964","tid":1108272,"uid":238697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T00:07:57.000Z","msg":"都幾可愛"},{"pid":"13bd2c777019fdd2528b874fa8e241699b13a053","tid":1108272,"uid":236691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T00:09:32.000Z","msg":"一出世就終點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2288d79102e2886a6a98444301439cbcb94380","tid":1108272,"uid":125128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T00:10:31.000Z","msg":"頭髮姐屌 幾個月都生翻啦"},{"pid":"c706efce45d45919c6cc54dc6d25f017e4f054b2","tid":1108272,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d18b20ca6beb2d447662d8f69eb2694a43aa964","tid":1108272,"uid":238697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T00:07:57.000Z","msg":"都幾可愛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T03:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be48a28e5c88a3d701d11867b6234639dc8e784c","tid":1108272,"uid":30771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T03:10:51.000Z","msg":"呀媽嘅電動剃刀係拎嚟剃閪毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c29f204f77643a98d5b932df9bf4130ee7f48ece","tid":1108272,"uid":83907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T03:26:33.000Z","msg":"啲女人真係on9，乜都喊一餐"},{"pid":"cec08ec15fd13f35bd1b940b5582ffbab02e9243","tid":1108272,"uid":33788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c29f204f77643a98d5b932df9bf4130ee7f48ece","tid":1108272,"uid":83907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T03:26:33.000Z","msg":"啲女人真係on9，乜都喊一餐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T04:32:21.000Z","msg":